<package name="PICO-TH">
<description>Raspberry Pi Pico
This footprint accepts either a Pico or Pico W mounted using through-hole for 0.021 &lt;bold&gt;round&lt;/bold&gt; pins, not square header pins!
The debug pins can be wired together ti debug either style of board, or can be ignored if the debugger
is attached to pins soldered to the Pico itself and not connecting down to the mainboard.</description>
