<plain>
<text x="149.86" y="27.94" size="2.54" layer="94">ECU Mainboard Connecters</text>
<text x="116.84" y="73.66" size="1.778" layer="97">Notes:
 - For board routing convenience, 27C256 VCC is not connected.
   The +5 from the ECU comes in via VPP and 2 pins on JP1
 - !OE!_5V is not used: we use the HC11 R/!W! signal instead
</text>
</plain>
